#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:2 eff52b2da3e544a2a14738d865920efe
msgid "User Guide"
msgstr "用户指南"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:4 ae1106ca0161489f98832e7b7b65f9ff
msgid ""
"In-depth, topic-oriented guides covering TensorMesh's core concepts, "
"design choices, and how to wield each component."
msgstr "面向主题的深入指南，涵盖 TensorMesh 的核心概念、设计取舍，以及如何运用每一个组件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:10 0d3923532559442bbb794dfe328073fa
msgid "Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:14 6cbe2a74fc274b6880d6724ca7bf5612
msgid "What TensorMesh is, the FEM pipeline, and how the modules fit together."
msgstr "TensorMesh 是什么、有限元方法流水线，以及各模块如何协同工作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:16 856c00efd2e54c16b630d60fd6af84fa
msgid "Meshes"
msgstr "网格"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:20 84997aa3174149acb3993a20509cedcb
msgid "Build, inspect, and load/save meshes; per-node and per-cell data."
msgstr "构建、检查与加载/保存网格；逐节点与逐单元数据。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:22 1089ff4c9df24980979df2060c72156e
msgid "Elements & Quadrature"
msgstr "单元与求积"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:26 45e74ad401584477a03a079961a072d3
msgid ""
"The element zoo, basis functions, quadrature rules, and ordering "
"conventions."
msgstr "单元家族、基函数、求积规则以及排序约定。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:28 b12b266060a3468b9a6dd7580676b682
msgid "Forms"
msgstr "弱形式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:32 1b0fa79da7b84f938a1b3aac68d7c0ca
msgid "Write weak forms in pure Python via the three assembler base classes."
msgstr "通过三个装配器基类，用纯 Python 编写弱形式。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:34 75a2802add32423e83a9f26997fa2621
msgid "Boundary Conditions"
msgstr "边界条件"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:38 110f4031071c4e83b3bc9d5ea49734ae
msgid "Apply Dirichlet BCs via static condensation; handle Neumann naturally."
msgstr "通过静态凝聚施加狄利克雷边界条件；自然地处理诺伊曼边界条件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:40 7497a16bbaf840088525d737bfff0a90
msgid "Sparse Solvers"
msgstr "稀疏求解器"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:44 324c3afb6d8246aebf3a7bd9b6d07098
msgid ""
"Linear and nonlinear sparse solves via torch-sla — five backends, batched"
" RHS, Newton / Picard / Anderson."
msgstr "通过 torch-sla 进行线性与非线性稀疏求解——五种后端、batch 右端项，以及 Newton / Picard / Anderson 方法。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:46 f2302dafd06146b1afcd999c97de8f7a
msgid "Time Integration"
msgstr "时间积分"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:50 9d1bf1a1296147bf9bd559f83797c641
