msgstr "用于瞬态问题的显式与隐式线性龙格-库塔格式。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:52 07a055a845dd4bd39bb3e22f72241ba1
msgid "Batched Workflows"
msgstr "批量化工作流"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:56 d2003821e0ce4fc6997967aa58babd3b
msgid "Three axes of batching: memory chunking, batched RHS, and ML datasets."
msgstr "批量化的三个维度：内存分块、batch 右端项，以及机器学习数据集。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:58 252a8c37e5634569bbbf06fa2444ffe8
msgid "Differentiability"
msgstr "可微性"

#: ../../source/user_guide/index.rst:62 395ff30ded094463ac04c04823260f18
msgid ""
"End-to-end gradients through assemble → solve, for inverse problems and "
"topology opt."
msgstr "贯穿 assemble → solve 的端到端梯度，用于反问题与拓扑优化。"
